OL,3,CSole Kingsmill survivor calls for
OL,4,Cpublic inquiry after 'disappointing
OL,5,Cinquest'
OL,7,FThere must be a public inquiry into
OL,8,Fthe Kingsmill murders, the sole
OL,9,Fsurvivor of the atrocity has said,
OL,10,Fexpressing disappointment after a
OL,11,F"Band-Aid inquest".
OL,13,FAlan Black was shot a number of times
OL,14,Fand left for dead among 10 of his
OL,15,Fslain workmates on a Co Armagh
OL,16,Froadside on January 5, 1976.
OL,18,FThe long-running inquest on Friday
OL,19,Ffound the shooting dead of the 10
OL,20,FProtestant workmen was an "overtly
OL,21,Fsectarian attack by the IRA".
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@RO]|D@[OU}D@\O]
