OL,3,CSole Kingsmill survivor calls for
OL,4,Cpublic inquiry after 'disappointing
OL,5,Cinquest'
OL,7,FCoroner Brian Sherrard said there had
OL,8,Fbeen no recognition from the
OL,9,Fperpetrators or their representatives
OL,10,Fof the "utter wrongness" of the attack.
OL,12,FSpeaking outside Belfast Coroner's
OL,13,FCourt on Friday, Mr Black said he is
OL,14,Fstill searching for the truth,
OL,15,Fdescribing the inquest as a "Band-Aid".
OL,17,FHe said: "I am so disappointed with
OL,18,Fthis inquest.
OL,26,@rD@HOUrD@XO]wD@]OUwD@fO]yD@JOU
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G2/13
