OL,3,CSole Kingsmill survivor calls for
OL,4,Cpublic inquiry after 'disappointing
OL,5,Cinquest'
OL,7,F"At every turn of the way they have
OL,8,Fhidden behind national security. These
OL,9,Fmurders happened 48 years ago, what on
OL,10,Fearth, how can national security be
OL,11,Fcompromised by murders that happened
OL,12,F48 years ago. It beggars belief.
OL,14,F"We're not anywhere near the truth. We
OL,15,Fneed a public inquiry. I would call on
OL,16,Feveryone that has a friend that got
OL,17,Fhurt to back us in getting this public
OL,18,Finquiry because we're never going to
OL,19,Fget the truth without it.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G3/13
