OL,5,Cinquest'
OL,7,F"This has been a Band-Aid, that's all
OL,8,Fand it has left us all so
OL,9,Fdissatisfied."
OL,11,FMr Black also expressed his
OL,12,Ffrustrations with the Irish
OL,13,FGovernment, saying they had questions
OL,14,Fto answer about the shootings, which
OL,15,Ftook place close to the border.
