OL,4,Cpublic inquiry after 'disappointing
OL,5,Cinquest'
OL,7,F"It's frustrating, counting all the
OL,8,Fpreliminary inquests, we're at this
OL,9,Fabout 10 years now. I was a young 70
OL,10,Fwhen I started out with this, now I'm
OL,11,Fold, 80, and I'm still as frustrated
OL,12,Fas I was back then, and it's not
OL,13,Fgetting any easier," he said.
OL,15,FAsked about the lack of engagement by
OL,16,Fthe IRA with the inquest, Mr Black
OL,17,Fresponded: "Why would they?
OL,19,F"Why would they implicate
OL,20,Fthemselves... turkeys don't vote for
OL,21,FChristmas.
