OL,3,CSole Kingsmill survivor calls for
OL,4,Cpublic inquiry after 'disappointing
OL,5,Cinquest'
OL,7,F"Kingsmill is something they're
OL,8,Ftotally ashamed of. They don't know
OL,9,Fhow to handle it.
OL,11,F"Now that the inquest is over and was
OL,12,Fso unsatisfactory, we really want the
OL,13,Fhelp of our elected representatives
OL,14,Fand everyone of good will to get
OL,15,Fbehind us and really support us in
OL,16,Fcalling for a public inquiry."
