OL,7,FMr Black was supported by his
OL,8,Fsolicitor, Barry O'Donnell, Karen
OL,9,FArmstrong, brother of John McConville
OL,10,Fwho was killed in the Kingsmill
OL,11,Fattack, former UUP MLA Danny Kennedy
OL,12,Fand a number of DUP representatives
OL,13,Foutside court.
OL,15,FMr Kennedy echoed his call for a
OL,16,Fpublic inquiry, and said all public
OL,17,Frepresentatives should demand of
OL,18,FNorthern Ireland Secretary Chris
OL,19,FHeaton-Harris that he grant a full
OL,20,Findependent public inquiry.
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G7/13
