OL,3,CSole Kingsmill survivor calls for
OL,4,Cpublic inquiry after 'disappointing
OL,5,Cinquest'
OL,7,F"That these issues can be finally
OL,8,Fexplored properly and independently
OL,9,Fbecause I think the justice system has
OL,10,Fdenied us, the inquest has failed us,
OL,11,Fthe security services have betrayed us
OL,12,Fand the Irish Government are nothing
OL,13,Fmore than contemptible hypocrites,
OL,14,Fthat's how we feel today as we leave
OL,15,Fthis court," he added.
OL,17,FMs Armstrong said they had felt a big
OL,18,Fresponsibility to keep going with the
OL,19,Finquest across almost a decade and
OL,20,Fsaid they felt they had to see it
OL,21,Fthrough.
