OL,7,F"It was a hard afternoon listening to
OL,8,Fthe graphics of that awful night, and
OL,9,Fat this stage we would like to call
OL,10,Ffor a public inquiry," she said.
OL,12,FEarlier in a joint statement, the
OL,13,FMcConville and Black families were
OL,14,Fcritical of a decision by the coroner
OL,15,Fnot to name two dead suspects.
