OL,7,FThey said: "We were distressed that
OL,8,Fthe coroner could not name two
OL,9,Fdeceased suspects who were suspected
OL,10,Fto have been involved in the murder of
OL,11,FJohn and his colleagues and the
OL,12,Fattempted murder of Alan Black.
OL,14,F"All suspects in the case were
OL,15,Fallocated cipher references to both
OL,16,Fidentify and protect their anonymity
OL,17,Fduring the inquest process."
