OL,7,FThey added: "Concealing the names of
OL,8,Fdead suspects leads only to conjecture
OL,9,Fand misinformation, rumour and
OL,10,Fsuspicion, which the inquest system
OL,11,Fshould serve to dispel and allay.
OL,13,F"We are also gravely concerned that
OL,14,Fthere are persons suspected to have
OL,15,Fbeen involved in the Kingsmill
OL,16,Fmassacre who are being protected by
OL,17,Fthe Crown for a wider political
OL,18,Fpurpose."
