OL,7,FThe families said they intend to make
OL,8,Frepresentations to Mr Heaton-Harris in
OL,9,Fthe following days to demand a public
OL,10,Finquiry.
OL,12,FThe legal firm representing the two
OL,13,Ffamilies said the inquest proceedings
OL,14,Fhad shown "collusion had no
OL,15,Fboundaries" during the Troubles.
OL,17,FThe KRW Law statement said: "The
OL,18,Fverdict and findings of the inquest
OL,19,Ftoday represent the next stage on a
OL,20,Ffraught legal journey.
